@frankchn @wolffg @MarkDaoust 
However, the notebook is just to show how to use my two main contributions, i.e., `tensorflow/python/util/get_layer_names.py` and `tensorflow/python/util/get_variable_values.py`. These two are the main features, which automatically extracts Parameters of the model from a saved model.
